msgid ""
"If a crate is currently running this framework, its dev-dependencies will be "
"semver-merged with the frameworks's `framework.dependencies`. However, this "
"may not be strictly necessary. Custom derives have a similar problem and "
"they solve it by just asking users to import the correct crate."
msgstr ""

